{"route":{"route":"/posts/77d15527/","outputPath":"posts/77d15527/index.html","kind":"post","title":"python使用lxml分析网页","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"77d15527"}},"post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/python使用lxml分析网页.md","route":"/posts/77d15527/","abbrlink":"77d15527","title":"python使用lxml分析网页","date":"2018-08-07 14:47:51","updated":"2018-08-07 14:47:51","tags":["python","编程"],"categories":["python"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"首先得引入lxml\n\n```python\n#xpath为\nfrome lxml import etree\n#cssselector为\nimport lxml.html\n#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少\n```\n\ncssselector\n\n```python\ntree = lxml.html.fromstring('你获取的网页源代码文件或变量')\ncss = tree.cssselect('要选择的内容')\n\n#例如tree.cssselect('div.word-info > div.pronounces > span.word-audio')\n#选择器选择的结果为list\n\ncss.text_content()\n\n#表示选择的内容\n\ncss.attrib['要表示的标签属性']\n\n#如css.attrb['class']表示的就是所选择内容的class属性\n```","excerptHtml":"<p>首先得引入lxml</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#xpath为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">frome lxml <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> etree</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> lxml.html</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>cssselector</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">tree = lxml.html.fromstring(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;你获取的网页源代码文件或变量&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css = tree.cssselect(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要选择的内容&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#例如tree.cssselect(&#x27;div.word-info &gt; div.pronounces &gt; span.word-audio&#x27;)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#选择器选择的结果为list</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.text_content()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#表示选择的内容</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.attrib[<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要表示的标签属性&#x27;</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#如css.attrb[&#x27;class&#x27;]表示的就是所选择内容的class属性</span></span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"首先得引入lxml\n\n```python\n#xpath为\nfrome lxml import etree\n#cssselector为\nimport lxml.html\n#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少\n```\n\ncssselector\n\n```python\ntree = lxml.html.fromstring('你获取的网页源代码文件或变量')\ncss = tree.cssselect('要选择的内容')\n\n#例如tree.cssselect('div.word-info > div.pronounces > span.word-audio')\n#选择器选择的结果为list\n\ncss.text_content()\n\n#表示选择的内容\n\ncss.attrib['要表示的标签属性']\n\n#如css.attrb['class']表示的就是所选择内容的class属性\n```\n\n\n**如果选择的内容换行符太多可以使用split表示成list去除**\n\n|说明|例子|\n|----|----|\n|选择所有标签|*|\n|选择<a\\>标签|a|\n|选择所有class=\"link\"的标签|.link|\n|选择class=\"link\"的<a\\>标签|a.link|\n|选择id=\"home\"的<a\\>标签|a#home|\n|选择父元素为<a\\>标签的所有<span\\>标签|a > span|\n|选择<a\\>标签内部的所有<span\\>标签|a span|\n|选择title属性为”Home”的所有<a\\>标签|a[title=Home]|\n\nxpath\n\n```python\nselector=etree.HTML('你获取的网页源代码文件或变量')\ncss = selector.xpath('要选择的内容')\n#xpath可直接表示\n#xpath可选择并表示属性\n```\n\n_xpath由于内容太多,可以直接参考官方文档_","bodyHtml":"<p>首先得引入lxml</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#xpath为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">frome lxml <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> etree</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> lxml.html</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>cssselector</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">tree = lxml.html.fromstring(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;你获取的网页源代码文件或变量&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css = tree.cssselect(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要选择的内容&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#例如tree.cssselect(&#x27;div.word-info &gt; div.pronounces &gt; span.word-audio&#x27;)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#选择器选择的结果为list</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.text_content()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#表示选择的内容</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.attrib[<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要表示的标签属性&#x27;</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#如css.attrb[&#x27;class&#x27;]表示的就是所选择内容的class属性</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>如果选择的内容换行符太多可以使用split表示成list去除</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th>例子</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>选择所有标签</td>\n<td>*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择&lt;a&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择所有class=&quot;link&quot;的标签</td>\n<td>.link</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择class=&quot;link&quot;的&lt;a&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a.link</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择id=&quot;home&quot;的&lt;a&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a#home</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择父元素为&lt;a&gt;标签的所有&lt;span&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a &gt; span</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择&lt;a&gt;标签内部的所有&lt;span&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a span</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>选择title属性为”Home”的所有&lt;a&gt;标签</td>\n<td>a[title=Home]</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>xpath</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">selector=etree.HTML(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;你获取的网页源代码文件或变量&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css = selector.xpath(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要选择的内容&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#xpath可直接表示</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#xpath可选择并表示属性</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><em>xpath由于内容太多,可以直接参考官方文档</em></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"首先得引入lxml\n\n```python\n#xpath为\nfrome lxml import etree\n#cssselector为\nimport lxml.html\n#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少\n```\n\ncssselector\n\n```python\ntree = lxml.html.fromstring('你获取的网页源代码文件或变量')\ncss = tree.cssselect('要选择的内容')\n\n#例如tree.cssselect('div.word-info > div.pronounces > span.word-audio')\n#选择器选择的结果为list\n\ncss.text_content()\n\n#表示选择的内容\n\ncss.attrib['要表示的标签属性']\n\n#如css.attrb['class']表示的就是所选择内容的class属性\n```\n\n<!--more-->\n**如果选择的内容换行符太多可以使用split表示成list去除**\n\n|说明|例子|\n|----|----|\n|选择所有标签|*|\n|选择<a\\>标签|a|\n|选择所有class=\"link\"的标签|.link|\n|选择class=\"link\"的<a\\>标签|a.link|\n|选择id=\"home\"的<a\\>标签|a#home|\n|选择父元素为<a\\>标签的所有<span\\>标签|a > span|\n|选择<a\\>标签内部的所有<span\\>标签|a span|\n|选择title属性为”Home”的所有<a\\>标签|a[title=Home]|\n\nxpath\n\n```python\nselector=etree.HTML('你获取的网页源代码文件或变量')\ncss = selector.xpath('要选择的内容')\n#xpath可直接表示\n#xpath可选择并表示属性\n```\n\n_xpath由于内容太多,可以直接参考官方文档_\n","plainText":"首先得引入lxml cssselector 如果选择的内容换行符太多可以使用split表示成list去除 说明 例子 选择所有标签 选择 标签 a 选择所有class=\"link\"的标签 .link 选择class=\"link\"的 标签 a.link 选择id=\"home\"的 标签 a home 选择父元素为 标签的所有 标签 a span 选择 标签内部的所有 标签 a span 选择title属性为”Home”的所有 标签 a[title=Home] xpath xpath由于内容太多,可以直接参考官方文档","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"77d15527","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}